org.conqat.lib.simulink.builder

Class ModelBuildingParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.lib.simulink.builder.ModelBuildingParameters

  • public class ModelBuildingParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Parameter class that controls how certain cases during model building should be handled. The default values provided during initialization already are a useful starting point.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      ModelBuildingParameters()
      Creates a new instance of model building parameters with the following default values: Preserve unconnected lines: false Charset: platform default Guess MDL encoding: true Logger: SimpleLogger (console) Reference lookup directories: JVM working directory.
